descriptive stats judge, Exp 1

accuracy by quant and model

agg_acc <- aggregate(correct~quantifier+degree_quantifier+model_judge, data=trimmed_data_exp1_judge_excl_control, function(x) {c(mean(x),sd(x)/sqrt(length(x)))})
ses_acc <- aggregate(correct~quantifier+degree_quantifier+model_judge, data=trimmed_data_exp1_judge_excl_control, function(x) {sd(x)/sqrt(length(x))})
agg_acc
##     quantifier degree_quantifier model_judge   correct.1   correct.2
## 1  exactly_one                no     0-model 0.976510067 0.008788222
## 2           no                no     0-model 0.950331126 0.012522654
## 3 at_least_one               yes     0-model 0.973063973 0.009410043
## 4  at_most_one               yes     0-model 0.546762590 0.029910411
## 5  exactly_one                no   1-2-model 0.944723618 0.009360500
## 6           no                no   1-2-model 0.961730449 0.007832091
## 7 at_least_one               yes   1-2-model 0.930860034 0.010426677
## 8  at_most_one               yes   1-2-model 0.912013536 0.011662256
acc_aggregated<-cbind(agg_acc,ses_acc[,4], agg_acc[,4])
acc_aggregated <- acc_aggregated %>% select(-one_of('correct', '2')) 

## acc for controls
control_agg_acc <- aggregate(correct~quantifier+degree_quantifier+model_judge, data=trimmed_data_exp1_judge_control_only, function(x) {c(mean(x),sd(x)/sqrt(length(x)))})
control_agg_acc

ses_control_acc <- aggregate(correct~quantifier+degree_quantifier+model_judge, data=trimmed_data_exp1_judge_control_only, function(x) {sd(x)/sqrt(length(x))})
ses_control_acc
##     quantifier degree_quantifier model_judge    correct

control_acc_aggregated<-cbind(control_agg_acc,ses_control_acc[,4], control_agg_acc[,4])
control_acc_aggregated <- control_acc_aggregated %>% select(-one_of('correct', '2'))

plot accuracy

#change labels of grouping factor for facet_wrap
degree_names <- as_labeller(
     c(`no` = "non-degree", `yes` = "degree"))
gp_rt <- ggplot(acc_aggregated, aes(x=quantifier, y=correct , fill=model, group=model))+
  geom_col(position = "dodge")+ geom_errorbar(aes(ymin=correct-se, ymax=correct+se), width=.2,
                 position=position_dodge(.9)) +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 35, hjust = 1), text = element_text(size=20))+
  #theme(axis.text.x = element_blank())+
  #ylim(210, 420)+
  ylab("accuracy (and standard errors)")+
  ####NB: check whether it is actually ms
  #scale_x_discrete(labels=c("Außer dem markierten","ist","QUANTIFIER","weiteres", "Dreieck","rot."))+
  #theme(legend.position = c(0.68, 0.85), legend.title = element_blank())+
  theme(axis.title=element_text(size=16,face="bold"))+
  facet_wrap(~degree_quantifier, labeller = degree_names, nrow = 1,scales = "free_x")
gp_rt

do a plot of the sentence RTs

plots_dir<- file.path(getwd(),"plots")
if(!dir.exists(plots_dir)) dir.create(plots_dir, recursive = TRUE, showWarnings = FALSE)

gp_rt <- ggplot(rt_aggregated, aes(x=roi, y=sentenceRT, colour=quantifier, group=quantifier))+
  geom_line()+ geom_point()+
  geom_ribbon(aes(ymin=sentenceRT-se, ymax=sentenceRT+se), linetype=0, alpha=0.1)+
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 35, hjust = 1), text = element_text(size=20))+
  #theme(axis.text.x = element_blank())+
  #ylim(210, 420)+
  ylab("reading time in ms\n(and std. errors)")+
  scale_x_discrete(labels=c("Besides the marked","is","QUANTIFIER","more", "triangle","red."))+
  #theme(legend.position = c(0.68, 0.85), legend.title = element_blank())+
  theme(axis.title=element_text(size=16,face="bold"))
